 />\n成身一定痴到"},{"pid":"a815ddb29af4bfc145f6eecc9f5ff1b6e7090544","tid":1738014,"uid":140115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:43:24.000Z","msg":"我屋企前後左右都有機會係狗 所以想搬出黎<br />\n一諗到對住窗口大叫解散警隊 刻不容緩都唔得<br />\n成個人就抑壓 好似有野阻止我做正確嘅事咁<br />\n上星期有5日都唔向屋企瞓 個人的確好舒服<br />\n但依家返番屋企瞓 個人又打回原形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀媽問做咩又唔返屋企 我直接話 因為唔想返<br />\n一句到尾 好想搬出去"},{"pid":"fcd6cd6fab52f50616d90d3535be40ae1c718c85","tid":1738014,"uid":176728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身同兩老其中一個關係已經好差<br />\n一路為左陪另一個一路都無搬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但近呢幾個月聽埋D類荷蘭叻偉論都好想離開呢個屋企<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申東區返工絲</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d3d0b3c93ffdf3fe009715f98551b05d839ca27","tid":1738014,"uid":226620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"運動初頭兩老都無乜野既<br />\n依家一阻佢返工同理大屠城 就即刻藍絲上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好日唔埋叫埋啲廢老親戚上黎食飯 <br />\n係到講暴徒暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到我同家姐都唔敢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩男朋友屋企人收留左我幾晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3f30a79116667f18e65a3f5406a2288318978d","tid":1738014,"uid":113207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzHmA72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyzHmA72.png&h=bd5e65d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星期日幫佢地保管身分證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b757a656125355dfa0c464ce8931436524636f8","tid":1738014,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d443ecd2185f4b9a1421aa9fadcdc7ad96aa520f",